== WWF == According to the [[World Wide Fund for Nature]], the territory of [[Hungary]] almost exclusively covered by [[Pannonian mixed forests]].<ref>{{WWF ecoregion|id=pa0431|name=Pannonian mixed forests}}</ref>
Smaller northern areas are covered by [[Carpathian montane conifer forests]]<ref>{{WWF ecoregion|id=pa0504|name=Carpathian montane conifer forests}}</ref>
== FEOW == According to the [[Freshwater Ecoregions Of the World]] Hungary is covered by the following ecoregions: * [[Upper Danube ecoregion]] <ref>[http://www.feow.org/ecoregion_details.php?eco=417 FEOW ref417] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505125825/http://www.feow.org/ecoregion_details.php?eco=417 |date=2014-05-05 }}</ref> * [[Dniester-Lower Danube ecoregion]] <ref>[http://www.feow.org/ecoregion_details.php?eco=418 FEOW ref418] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320191340/http://www.feow.org/ecoregion_details.php?eco=418 |date=2014-03-20 }}</ref>
