'''''Nahiyah''''' ({{Lang-ar|ناحية}}) or subdistrict is the third-level [[administrative division]] in [[Iraq]].
Iraq is divided into 18 ''[[Muhafazah]]'' ({{Lang-ar|محافظة}}) (See: [[Governorates of Iraq]]) which are divided into more than 130 ''[[Kaza]]'' ({{Lang-ar|قضاء}}) (See: [[Districts of Iraq]]). These districts are divided into subdistricts.
